high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the small counter space between the refrigerator and the stove.
Pick up the spoon to the right of the knife, on the counter top.
Go to the refrigerator on your left.
Place the spoon in the white coffee cup on the left side of the second shelf of the refrigerator.
Remove the coffee cup with the spoon inside it, from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go across the room to the door and turn right, then go to the small, black stand across from you.
Place the cup with the spoon inside it, on the back, right corner of the black stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a coffee cup containing a spoon on the black stand.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter on the right in between the fridge and the stove.
Pick up the spoon to the right of the knife on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on the right.
Put the spoon inside the white mug inside the fridge on the bottom left shelf.
Pick up the mug with the spoon inside from the shelf and close the doors.
Turn around and hang a right at the wall to reach the small black table.
Place the chilled mug with the spoon in the back right corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold mug with a spoon on a table.

high_descs: walk to face counter to the right of the fridge
pick up spoon from the counter
walk left to face fridge
put spoon into mug inside fridge
pick up mug from inside fridge
walk to face black shelves to left of white table
put mug onto black shelves
anns.task_desc: put mug and spoon onto black shelves
